main (1771) <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=dIdYAAAAcAAJ&amp;pg=PA165">M\xc3\xa9moire pour les libraires associ\xc3\xa9s \xc3\xa0 l\'Encyclop\xc3\xa9die: contre le sieur Luneau de Boisjermain</a>.</i> p. 165.</span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/wiki/Philipp_Blom" title="Philipp Blom">Philipp Blom</a>. <i>Encyclop\xc3\xa9die: the triumph of reason in an unreasonable age Fourth Estate</i>, 2004. p. 37</span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-12"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">"<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=9OMTAAAAQAAJ&amp;pg=PA70">Prospectus du Dictionnaire de Chambers, traduit en Fran\xc3\xa7ois, et propos\xc3\xa9 par souscription</a>" in: M. Desfontaines. <i>Jugemens sur quelques ouvrages nouveaux.</i> Vol 8. (1745). p. 72</span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=eX9KAAAAcAAJ&amp;pg=PA934">Review</a> in: <i>M\xc3\xa9moires pour l\'histoire des sciences et des beaux arts</i>, May 1745, Nr. 2. pp. 934\xe2\x80\x9338</span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><i>Mercure Journal</i> (1745, p. 87) cited in: Lough (1971), p. 20</span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-15"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Mills\' summary of this matter was published in <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pierre-Joseph_Luneau_de_Boisjermain" class="extiw" title="fr:Pierre-Joseph Luneau de Boisjermain">Boisjermain</a>\'s <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com